data.description: Beautiful setting for this large 2-story farmhouse on 17.85 acres.  In need of some TLC.  There are 2 detached, 2 stall garages (One garage is 20 x 25 and the other garage is 20 x 18).  Approximately 8.5 wooded acres, 9.35 tillable acres.  Public water and sewer.  Seller willing to subdivide.  So much room to run and play!
